entry.value: SELECT CASE WHEN evt.IMO < 0 THEN CONVERT(NVARCHAR(10), '') ELSE CONVERT(NVARCHAR(10), evt.IMO) END as imo_no, evt.MMSI as mmsi_no, evt.ShipName as ship_name, evt.CallSign as callsign, '' as coordinate, '' as door_status, evt.TimeStmp as timestamp, '' as photo, '' as flag, evt.lng as longitude, evt.lat as latitude, evt.SOG as sog, evt.COG as cog, alm.AlarmMsg as message, evt.Info as info, evt.ZoneID as zone_id, zon.ZoneName as zone_name, '' as aging FROM Events evt LEFT JOIN Alarms alm on alm.AlarmID = evt.AlarmID LEFT JOIN Zones zon on zon.ZoneID = evt.ZoneID WHERE EventID=${EventID}

entry.value: SELECT ( SELECT Top 1 EventID FROM Events WHERE MMSI = ${MMSI} and AlarmID = 5 Order By TimeStmp DESC ) as transaction_id, CASE WHEN evt.IMO < 0 THEN CONVERT(NVARCHAR(10), '') ELSE CONVERT(NVARCHAR(10), evt.IMO) END as imo_no, evt.MMSI as mmsi_no, evt.ShipName as ship_name, evt.CallSign as callsign, evt.ETA as eta, '' as ata, '' as etd, '' as atd, '' as last_port_of_call, '' as next_port_of_call, '' as dg_on_board, '' as purpose_of_call, '' as mean_draft_arrival, '' as status FROM Events evt LEFT JOIN Alarms alm on alm.AlarmID = evt.AlarmID LEFT JOIN Zones zon on zon.ZoneID = evt.ZoneID WHERE EventID=${EventID}
